f</span><span class=\"bp\">⁻¹'</span> <span class=\"n\">t</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Again, if I place this in the continuous_on file it would require more imports so I am not sure where to place this</p>",
